WEBVTT

01:37.800 --> 01:40.590
[Fate Chooses You]

01:41.370 --> 01:43.770
[Episode 23]

02:33.840 --> 02:34.440
Watch out!

02:42.310 --> 02:43.030
Mr. Gui

02:43.630 --> 02:44.560
was killed by me.

02:45.030 --> 02:46.160
If you have the guts,

02:46.170 --> 02:47.370
come and take my life.

03:09.800 --> 03:12.210
Be good and come back
to Qianyan Cave with us,

03:12.210 --> 03:13.640
and you'll suffer less.

03:32.910 --> 03:33.870
You once told me

03:34.840 --> 03:36.120
your master sent you down the mountain

03:36.120 --> 03:37.190
to find your path

03:37.750 --> 03:39.190
and survive your tribulation.

03:39.190 --> 03:39.590
Yes.

03:40.520 --> 03:41.520
Then does slaying demons

03:41.520 --> 03:42.579
count as your path?

03:42.910 --> 03:43.800
Does saving people

03:43.800 --> 03:45.060
count as your path too?

03:45.310 --> 03:46.710
They abandon mothers and keep sons,

03:46.710 --> 03:48.910
raise Gu to harm others, murder and rob,

03:49.280 --> 03:50.470
have no moral principles,

03:50.470 --> 03:51.930
and disregard blood ties.

03:52.310 --> 03:54.040
They claim territory as kings,

03:54.280 --> 03:55.430
and in that tiny place,

03:55.430 --> 03:56.630
commit the filthiest,

03:56.630 --> 03:58.290
most shady deeds in the world.

03:59.190 --> 04:00.150
How are they

04:00.560 --> 04:02.090
any different from demons?

04:02.400 --> 04:03.630
They are even worse.

04:05.030 --> 04:05.750
So,

04:07.120 --> 04:08.050
you must help me.

04:09.240 --> 04:10.150
I need you.

05:18.430 --> 05:19.760
What do you want me to do?

05:23.430 --> 05:25.690
I want you to be the sharp blade
in my hand,

05:25.880 --> 05:27.040
piercing the sky

05:27.040 --> 05:28.430
that covers hell.

05:29.390 --> 05:31.320
I want a beam of light to shine down,

05:31.430 --> 05:33.310
illuminating all those demons

05:33.360 --> 05:34.560
and burning them

05:35.310 --> 05:36.640
with nowhere to escape.

08:39.549 --> 08:40.440
Sheng,

08:41.120 --> 08:43.000
I haven't seen you for so many years.

08:43.000 --> 08:45.390
You really have improved a lot.

09:19.190 --> 09:19.740
Jin Lun!

09:43.510 --> 09:44.640
What a coincidence.

09:44.870 --> 09:45.840
We meet again.

09:46.960 --> 09:48.290
It's not a coincidence.

10:00.550 --> 10:02.480
This place is called Wushui Cliff.

10:02.750 --> 10:04.020
It is thousands of feet high

10:04.020 --> 10:04.950
and bottomless.

10:05.840 --> 10:07.510
Although it is called
Wushui (without water),

10:07.510 --> 10:09.170
it's worse than having water.

10:09.550 --> 10:10.480
What do you mean?

10:11.120 --> 10:12.720
It's densely covered with insects.

10:12.720 --> 10:14.440
Even Void Stage masters

10:14.440 --> 10:15.510
who stumble in

10:15.530 --> 10:16.990
will struggle to survive.

10:33.120 --> 10:34.240
Just you?

10:34.750 --> 10:35.510
It's us.

10:51.320 --> 10:53.520
Golden Bracelet of Demon Suppression.

10:54.030 --> 10:55.840
Tianyin Mountain's treasure

10:56.250 --> 10:57.710
is actually in your hands.

10:58.360 --> 11:00.560
Such a treasure falling into your hands

11:00.790 --> 11:02.360
is really a waste.

11:03.080 --> 11:04.880
Legend has it that this bracelet

11:04.910 --> 11:07.720
can summon the power
of the Divine Dragon and White Tiger

11:07.720 --> 11:10.670
and crush the flesh and blood
of those who enter the formation.

11:10.670 --> 11:12.130
But your skill is lacking.

11:12.510 --> 11:14.670
You are merely all show and no substance.

11:14.670 --> 11:16.870
Although I don't have
the Divine Dragon and White Tiger,

11:16.870 --> 11:18.530
I have the Yuanyi Twin Swords.

12:06.360 --> 12:07.560
Can you still hold on?

12:08.510 --> 12:09.240
I'm fine.

12:10.440 --> 12:11.320
Sheng,

12:11.480 --> 12:13.410
do you want to kill your own father?

12:34.390 --> 12:35.390
He is your father?

12:36.200 --> 12:37.000
Sheng,

12:37.870 --> 12:39.320
didn't you tell your friend

12:39.320 --> 12:40.320
your story?

12:41.240 --> 12:41.790
Why?

12:42.200 --> 12:45.330
Do you also agree
that patricide violates moral ethics,

12:45.440 --> 12:47.720
something you're ashamed to even speak of?

12:47.720 --> 12:48.630
Father?

12:49.440 --> 12:50.440
Do you deserve it?

12:51.240 --> 12:52.240
For so many years,

12:52.390 --> 12:54.000
how many sons have you fathered

12:54.000 --> 12:55.930
and how many women have you harmed?

12:56.630 --> 12:57.670
I barely survived

12:57.670 --> 12:58.930
from my mother's womb,

12:59.120 --> 13:00.180
but I didn't expect

13:00.390 --> 13:01.550
that on the day I was born,

13:01.550 --> 13:02.360
I would fall into

13:02.360 --> 13:03.560
another devil's den.

13:03.840 --> 13:05.360
You look down on us

13:06.000 --> 13:07.360
as if we're nothing.

13:07.910 --> 13:09.080
In your eyes,

13:09.440 --> 13:11.030
all children are just

13:11.030 --> 13:13.560
your stepping stones
to ascend into godhood.

13:16.000 --> 13:17.630
In this Qianyan Cave,

13:18.600 --> 13:20.260
all ethics and familial bonds

13:20.360 --> 13:21.670
are cast aside.

13:23.480 --> 13:25.870
The father abandons his duty,
and children forsake theirs.

13:25.870 --> 13:27.630
How twisted and disgusting!

13:29.030 --> 13:30.230
Does a person like you

13:30.600 --> 13:32.260
deserve to be called a father?

13:38.600 --> 13:40.000
Whether I deserve it or not

13:40.000 --> 13:41.240
is not up to you.

13:41.870 --> 13:43.000
I gave you life

13:43.720 --> 13:45.200
and a place to stay.

13:46.030 --> 13:48.080
Even if you are full of resentment,

13:48.200 --> 13:49.550
even if you live by my side

13:49.550 --> 13:51.150
like a stray dog,

13:51.200 --> 13:52.960
you are still my child.

13:54.870 --> 13:57.630
Blood ties can't be severed.

13:58.910 --> 14:00.960
Even if you refuse to admit it,

14:01.910 --> 14:03.750
they will always exist.

14:08.270 --> 14:10.000
When I first escaped,

14:10.670 --> 14:12.470
I tossed and turned every night.

14:13.030 --> 14:14.510
My senior sister used to tell me stories

14:14.510 --> 14:15.510
to put me to sleep.

14:15.750 --> 14:16.750
In those stories,

14:17.550 --> 14:18.510
my favorite character

14:18.510 --> 14:19.270
was Nezha.

14:19.870 --> 14:20.870
To save the people, Nezha

14:20.870 --> 14:22.530
killed the Dragon King's son.

14:22.720 --> 14:24.870
But he was misunderstood by his father,

14:24.870 --> 14:26.030
who blamed him

14:26.030 --> 14:27.160
indiscriminately.

14:27.910 --> 14:29.870
Filled with grief and indignation, Nezha

14:29.870 --> 14:31.480
severed his bones to his father

14:31.480 --> 14:33.280
and rent his flesh to his mother.

14:33.750 --> 14:36.550
From then on, he severed
this ill-fated blood tie.

14:37.200 --> 14:38.440
I envy him

14:39.000 --> 14:40.860
for having such great abilities.

14:41.670 --> 14:42.550
Unlike me,

14:43.240 --> 14:45.040
even though I loathe you so much,

14:45.440 --> 14:46.000
I still have to

14:46.000 --> 14:48.260
live with this blood running in my veins.

14:49.240 --> 14:49.910
However,

14:50.240 --> 14:51.240
I later thought of

14:51.240 --> 14:52.480
a good idea.

14:53.550 --> 14:54.870
If you die,

14:55.550 --> 14:57.410
won't this bloodline be severed?

14:58.200 --> 14:59.030
So,

14:59.840 --> 15:01.870
for me to get a good night's sleep,

15:02.150 --> 15:03.440
please be merciful

15:03.440 --> 15:04.270
and just die.

15:05.080 --> 15:06.120
Jin Lun, help me!

16:01.480 --> 16:01.880
You...

16:02.960 --> 16:03.600
How is it?

16:04.510 --> 16:05.240
How does it feel

16:05.240 --> 16:07.170
to be wounded by the Bonding Curse?

16:07.410 --> 16:08.910
Do you feel desperate?

16:09.390 --> 16:10.520
Do you want to curse?

16:11.870 --> 16:12.630
When...

16:13.030 --> 16:14.160
When did you do this?

16:27.720 --> 16:28.320
Good.

16:29.360 --> 16:30.240
Very good.

16:31.240 --> 16:33.790
You truly are my daughter.

16:34.440 --> 16:35.470
Smart enough

16:35.960 --> 16:37.160
and ruthless enough.

16:46.440 --> 16:47.750
I'm going to kill you.

16:47.960 --> 16:49.000
I'll kill you!

16:51.490 --> 16:52.200
Then you must

16:52.200 --> 16:53.670
have the ability to do so.

16:54.440 --> 16:56.270
Times have changed.

16:56.810 --> 16:58.410
Now I'm the hunter,

16:58.440 --> 16:59.630
and you're the prey.

17:00.150 --> 17:02.030
Your life is in my hands.

17:02.240 --> 17:03.720
Do you have any other choice

17:03.720 --> 17:05.400
except for begging me to spare you?

17:05.400 --> 17:07.060
Do you think I'm afraid of you?

17:07.310 --> 17:07.829
Will you

17:08.440 --> 17:09.790
really sacrifice yourself for me

17:09.790 --> 17:11.030
and die with me?

17:11.720 --> 17:12.640
Sheng,

17:13.000 --> 17:13.680
I really

17:13.680 --> 17:15.280
underestimated you before.

17:15.550 --> 17:16.230
In fact,

17:16.230 --> 17:17.829
among the over 100 children,

17:18.270 --> 17:20.599
you're the one
who takes after me the most.

17:20.790 --> 17:21.790
Unfortunately,

17:22.810 --> 17:24.740
you've still got a long way to go.

17:39.400 --> 17:40.030
Jin Lun,

17:40.350 --> 17:41.350
kill him quickly.

17:41.550 --> 17:43.440
If I kill him, will you die?

17:46.350 --> 17:46.880
Sheng!

17:48.070 --> 17:49.030
Do it now.

17:49.310 --> 17:51.110
I can't hold him off much longer.

18:27.680 --> 18:28.160
Sheng!

18:29.000 --> 18:29.750
Do it now.

18:30.000 --> 18:30.480
Hurry!

18:30.790 --> 18:31.510
Hurry!

18:53.720 --> 18:54.520
It has worked.

19:00.960 --> 19:01.590
Jin Lun.

19:07.890 --> 19:11.190
♪ Hear the Gu curse
turn into cries for help ♪

19:11.250 --> 19:15.160
♪ Blood-stained hand, sword drawn ♪

19:13.680 --> 19:14.750
Jin Lun!

19:15.190 --> 19:18.660
♪ Trapped in Qianyan Cave ♪

19:18.690 --> 19:22.170
♪ Even hell must be broken free from ♪

19:21.070 --> 19:21.680
Jin Lun!

19:22.400 --> 19:23.240
Hold on to me!

19:23.300 --> 19:26.470
♪ With every stroke of hatred ♪

19:26.500 --> 19:30.510
♪ Let it grow into a dagger I wear ♪

19:30.530 --> 19:32.780
♪ No need to show me mercy there ♪

19:32.800 --> 19:36.640
♪ Let me take every blow ♪

19:38.260 --> 19:42.350
♪ Drag my wounds through the hollow road ♪

19:42.380 --> 19:45.660
♪ I'll pluck the passion
locked in my brow ♪

19:45.680 --> 19:49.050
♪ At the end of the mountains,
I pick up fireflies now ♪

19:49.070 --> 19:53.230
♪ Burn me down, I feel no pain ♪

19:53.270 --> 19:54.850
♪ I believe Heaven sees all ♪

19:54.870 --> 19:57.140
♪ Its wrath shines upon demons ♪

19:57.320 --> 20:00.700
♪ But who will show me mercy? ♪

20:00.870 --> 20:02.380
♪ I believe I'm innocent ♪

20:02.410 --> 20:07.710
♪ Turned into dust and scattered away ♪

20:04.920 --> 20:05.680
Jin Lun.

20:08.460 --> 20:10.040
♪ I accept the blame of
numerous accusations ♪

20:08.830 --> 20:09.960
Jin Lun!

20:10.060 --> 20:12.520
♪ I offer no defense ♪

20:12.550 --> 20:16.030
♪ I accept this as my only choice ♪

20:16.050 --> 20:17.690
♪ I admit my heart
is as hard as iron and stone ♪

20:17.710 --> 20:19.990
♪ Call me cold if you must ♪

20:20.130 --> 20:22.740
♪ Until I die ♪

20:23.280 --> 20:26.490
♪ I accept this trial of love
fate has given me ♪

20:26.730 --> 20:31.160
♪ I take in both love and hate alike ♪

21:08.240 --> 21:10.680
Soft white buns!

21:11.160 --> 21:11.960
Steamed buns!

21:13.090 --> 21:13.950
They look good.

21:14.400 --> 21:14.920
Sir.

21:15.480 --> 21:16.210
Have a taste.

21:16.790 --> 21:18.000
How much for the steamed buns?

21:18.000 --> 21:18.590
Take it.

21:19.030 --> 21:20.830
Three wen for one, and 5 wen for 2.

21:20.880 --> 21:21.940
That's expensive.

21:22.400 --> 21:23.440
You call this expensive?

21:23.440 --> 21:25.240
Can I get a discount if I buy more?

21:25.720 --> 21:26.850
How many do you want?

21:30.400 --> 21:31.070
All of them.

21:32.070 --> 21:32.750
All of them?

21:35.530 --> 21:37.160
Extracted from 3 taels of mint leaves,

21:37.160 --> 21:38.960
it's guaranteed to refresh your mind.

21:38.960 --> 21:39.960
It's not strong enough.

21:39.960 --> 21:40.680
Take a look around.

21:40.680 --> 21:41.940
See anything you like?

21:44.940 --> 21:46.200
This one is just right.

21:51.960 --> 21:53.550
This is a fine weapon.

21:56.310 --> 21:57.770
Have you made your choice?

21:57.790 --> 21:58.990
This feels very good.

22:14.110 --> 22:14.830
Master,

22:15.440 --> 22:18.300
are you willing to accept me
as your disciple today?

22:24.720 --> 22:25.510
Master.

22:25.920 --> 22:26.750
Master.

22:27.160 --> 22:28.550
If you don't agree today,

22:28.550 --> 22:30.210
I will ask you again tomorrow.

22:30.270 --> 22:30.830
Master.

22:32.920 --> 22:33.480
Master.

22:33.880 --> 22:35.680
Then I'll go sharpen your sword.

24:25.880 --> 24:26.440
Master.

24:46.400 --> 24:47.260
Welcome, Sirs.

24:47.400 --> 24:49.130
What kind of tea would you like?

24:52.590 --> 24:53.200
Sir,

24:53.720 --> 24:54.780
we are booking the whole place.

24:54.780 --> 24:56.440
Sorry for the inconvenience.

25:00.440 --> 25:01.700
Sorry for the trouble.

25:07.920 --> 25:11.990
[Sifang Teahouse]

25:10.110 --> 25:11.200
The Sihe Library

25:11.480 --> 25:13.270
opens once every 5 years.

25:13.640 --> 25:15.300
Each time it opens for 10 days.

25:15.510 --> 25:17.200
So we must memorize

25:17.590 --> 25:20.350
the complete "Unparalleled Secret Magic"
within 10 days.

25:20.350 --> 25:21.950
For this trip to North Xiang,

25:22.000 --> 25:23.400
we had 36 people in total,

25:23.750 --> 25:25.010
divided into 3 groups.

25:25.720 --> 25:26.550
But right now,

25:27.070 --> 25:28.270
only 20 have arrived.

25:29.030 --> 25:30.590
For those who didn't make it,

25:30.590 --> 25:32.310
I'm afraid they never will.

25:37.310 --> 25:38.680
Since we are here,

25:39.070 --> 25:40.640
we can't let them down.

25:41.480 --> 25:43.610
We have to memorize their parts as well

25:43.750 --> 25:45.400
and bring them back to the Central Plains.

25:45.400 --> 25:48.000
The "Unparalleled Secret Magic"
consists of 120 volumes.

25:48.000 --> 25:49.160
Astronomy, Calendar,

25:49.160 --> 25:51.720
Arithmetic, Craftsmanship, and Literature—

25:51.720 --> 25:53.650
the volumes of each category vary.

25:54.030 --> 25:56.070
Besides what was originally assigned,

25:56.070 --> 25:56.720
who else

25:57.240 --> 25:58.300
can memorize more?

26:02.640 --> 26:03.790
For the Astronomy volumes,

26:03.790 --> 26:05.240
I can memorize 3 more volumes.

26:05.240 --> 26:05.570
Okay.

26:07.030 --> 26:08.690
Chai Yu's 5 Astronomy volumes

26:09.120 --> 26:09.850
changed to 8.

26:15.160 --> 26:16.070
I'll cover

26:16.440 --> 26:17.840
all 24 Calendar volumes.

26:18.550 --> 26:19.070
Really?

26:20.050 --> 26:21.270
Don't force yourself.

26:21.270 --> 26:21.930
No problem.

26:22.200 --> 26:22.750
Trust me.

26:23.070 --> 26:23.440
Okay.

26:29.270 --> 26:31.830
I can memorize 5 more Astronomy volumes.

26:32.430 --> 26:34.890
That leaves Arithmetic and Craftsmanship.

26:35.510 --> 26:37.770
Who else can memorize a few more volumes?

26:38.000 --> 26:40.260
I can take 5 more Craftsmanship volumes.

26:42.000 --> 26:42.730
Arithmetic.

26:44.330 --> 26:45.730
I'll take 6 more volumes.

26:59.590 --> 27:02.510
These are Mind-Awakening Pills
from Chongling Valley,

27:02.510 --> 27:05.030
which can temporarily
boost your brainpower.

27:05.030 --> 27:06.920
It takes time for the effects to kick in,

27:06.920 --> 27:08.480
so everyone should take them

27:08.480 --> 27:09.510
before setting off.

27:09.510 --> 27:11.960
They will take effect
just as we arrive at the library.

27:11.960 --> 27:12.960
Please remember,

27:13.070 --> 27:14.400
although this medicine is potent,

27:14.400 --> 27:15.680
you must not take too many.

27:15.680 --> 27:17.410
A maximum of 3 pills per person.

27:17.960 --> 27:19.020
Any more than that,

27:19.200 --> 27:21.400
and your body won't be able to handle it.

27:36.440 --> 27:37.770
Why did you take so many?

27:38.310 --> 27:39.240
I'm getting old,

27:39.920 --> 27:41.120
and my memory is poor.

27:41.350 --> 27:43.610
Better safe than sorry with a few extras.

27:43.750 --> 27:44.750
I don't need them.

27:44.960 --> 27:45.820
I can remember.

27:47.750 --> 27:48.350
This time,

27:48.880 --> 27:49.700
no matter what,

27:49.700 --> 27:52.560
we must bring out
the "Unparalleled Secret Magic,"

27:52.810 --> 27:54.270
even if it costs our lives.

27:59.510 --> 28:00.110
Everyone,

28:01.750 --> 28:02.480
when

28:02.920 --> 28:04.680
the library closes,

28:05.270 --> 28:06.350
or when you feel

28:06.880 --> 28:07.920
that you can no longer memorize

28:07.920 --> 28:08.920
any more content,

28:09.110 --> 28:10.510
come straight back here.

28:11.310 --> 28:14.110
Lu Zhanying and the others
will provide pen and ink

28:14.160 --> 28:15.820
for everyone to write it down.

28:16.750 --> 28:18.150
We will always stay here.

28:18.400 --> 28:19.440
If you have any problems,

28:19.440 --> 28:20.370
just let us know.

28:28.550 --> 28:29.960
As you go forth,

28:30.960 --> 28:32.620
you will face many hardships.

28:33.830 --> 28:35.480
What we do today

28:36.720 --> 28:38.030
may cost us our lives

28:38.920 --> 28:41.200
and may not even leave a mark in history.

28:41.920 --> 28:43.050
But please believe,

28:43.830 --> 28:44.490
this battle

28:45.110 --> 28:46.920
is for the people of the world,

28:47.070 --> 28:48.640
for the future of our race.

28:50.510 --> 28:52.710
Your righteousness empowers our race.

28:53.200 --> 28:54.060
I, Tai Shiqian,

28:54.550 --> 28:55.810
pay my respects to you.

28:56.510 --> 28:57.510
Empower our race.

28:57.680 --> 28:58.680
No regrets even in death.

28:58.680 --> 29:01.550
-Empower our race. No regrets in death.
-Empower our race. No regrets in death.

29:01.550 --> 29:04.310
-Empower our race. No regrets in death.
-Empower our race. No regrets in death.

29:04.310 --> 29:08.710
-Empower our race. No regrets in death.
-Empower our race. No regrets in death.

29:13.400 --> 29:14.110
The library is open.

29:14.110 --> 29:14.680
Go, go.

29:14.680 --> 29:15.960
-Hurry. Hurry up.
-Go.

29:15.960 --> 29:16.860
The library is open. Let's go take a look.

29:16.860 --> 29:17.880
-Yes.
-Let's go.

29:32.350 --> 29:32.950
Everyone,

29:33.980 --> 29:36.180
the road to the revival of the Human Race

29:36.880 --> 29:38.400
begins here.

30:28.430 --> 30:34.490
[Sihe Library]

31:43.130 --> 31:44.720
[Unparalleled Secret Magic]
[Astronomy]

31:46.720 --> 31:47.850
Lord of Rust-Sword.

31:48.110 --> 31:49.110
Stop right there.

31:49.440 --> 31:49.920
One.

31:50.590 --> 31:51.030
Two.

31:53.750 --> 31:54.350
Zhanying.

31:55.270 --> 31:57.000
What are your orders this time?

31:57.750 --> 31:58.550
Let me ask you,

31:58.750 --> 32:01.150
where is the flower
I gave you this morning?

32:02.750 --> 32:03.610
I threw it away.

32:03.720 --> 32:04.520
Threw it away?

32:04.790 --> 32:06.050
Where did you throw it?

32:07.000 --> 32:07.930
It's right here.

32:10.120 --> 32:10.740
Zhanying,

32:11.110 --> 32:12.970
this flower is really beautiful.

32:14.720 --> 32:15.380
Beautiful.

32:17.550 --> 32:19.350
This mission is extraordinary.

32:19.640 --> 32:20.880
Sending them to the library

32:20.880 --> 32:22.590
is barely passing the first stage.

32:22.590 --> 32:24.590
If the people
from the immortal sect catch up,

32:24.590 --> 32:26.590
a fierce battle will be inevitable.

32:27.350 --> 32:28.210
I was wondering

32:28.400 --> 32:29.160
if we should send An

32:29.160 --> 32:30.110
somewhere else.

32:31.160 --> 32:31.820
I am a demon.

32:32.200 --> 32:33.550
I can protect myself.

32:34.080 --> 32:35.490
Don't be childish.

32:35.960 --> 32:37.490
A demon's life matters too.

32:37.680 --> 32:39.640
Whether sending you away
or taking you with us,

32:39.640 --> 32:41.240
it's all for you to live.

32:41.760 --> 32:43.170
If you die because of us,

32:43.200 --> 32:44.830
wouldn't that defeat the purpose?

32:44.830 --> 32:45.720
Then it would have been better

32:45.720 --> 32:46.980
not to bring you along.

32:48.110 --> 32:49.310
I don't want to leave.

32:50.790 --> 32:51.850
I don't have a home.

32:52.750 --> 32:54.310
I have nowhere to go.

32:55.720 --> 32:56.440
I don't know

32:56.440 --> 32:58.270
what big plan you are talking about,

32:58.270 --> 32:58.720
but

32:59.110 --> 33:00.480
since Master protects you,

33:00.480 --> 33:01.740
I will protect you too.

33:02.480 --> 33:04.140
Although my power is average,

33:04.440 --> 33:06.160
I can serve tea and water.

33:06.830 --> 33:07.510
At worst,

33:08.110 --> 33:10.640
I can grind ink, do chores,
and deliver meals.

33:13.750 --> 33:15.000
I won't cause you

33:15.000 --> 33:16.070
any trouble.

33:22.590 --> 33:23.190
All right.

33:23.680 --> 33:25.540
If she wants to stay, let her stay.

33:25.680 --> 33:26.940
She can just follow me.

33:27.440 --> 33:28.500
I will protect her.

33:29.160 --> 33:29.790
Then you'd better

33:29.790 --> 33:31.360
take her as your disciple soon.

33:31.360 --> 33:32.470
Otherwise, when this is over

33:32.470 --> 33:33.400
and we part ways,

33:33.990 --> 33:35.790
she'll have nowhere to go again.

33:42.030 --> 33:42.830
That won't do.

33:43.030 --> 33:44.750
I wade through blood
and corpses every day.

33:44.750 --> 33:45.720
How can I take her with me?

33:45.720 --> 33:46.830
Take her back to your home.

33:46.830 --> 33:48.510
That depends on whether An is willing.

33:48.510 --> 33:49.790
I think she just wants to follow you now.

33:49.790 --> 33:50.790
What should we do?

34:25.929 --> 34:27.320
Senior Sister asked you
to pass the message?

34:27.320 --> 34:29.179
Don't take risks. Come back soon.

34:29.280 --> 34:30.139
Come back soon.

34:30.190 --> 34:31.449
I'm worried about you.

34:31.489 --> 34:32.280
Where is she?

34:32.780 --> 34:33.510
Lead the way.

35:02.530 --> 35:02.960
I...

35:04.960 --> 35:05.320
Sir.

35:05.880 --> 35:06.920
What's the rush?

35:12.150 --> 35:14.030
-Great! Great!
-Great! Great!

35:14.670 --> 35:15.840
-Great!
-Great!

35:16.290 --> 35:18.420
Yes, drink more with the young master.

35:20.920 --> 35:22.280
Come again next time!

35:23.920 --> 35:24.550
How about

35:24.840 --> 35:26.040
we go inside and look?

35:26.760 --> 35:27.890
How could he be here?

35:28.110 --> 35:29.280
In the Young Sect Master's heart,

35:29.280 --> 35:30.810
there is only Senior Jiang.

35:31.310 --> 35:32.340
It's impossible for him to be there.

35:32.340 --> 35:34.280
[Tianxiang Restaurant]

35:36.070 --> 35:38.330
-Young Sect Master?
-Young Sect Master?

35:57.030 --> 35:57.630
Xu Feng sent a letter, saying

35:57.630 --> 35:58.800
Lin Muhan has been found.

35:58.800 --> 36:00.000
He is in Phoenix City.

36:00.320 --> 36:01.250
In Phoenix City?

36:01.550 --> 36:02.880
Where did they find him?

36:03.020 --> 36:03.820
It didn't say.

36:04.080 --> 36:05.220
But it said those
from the Wushuang Society

36:05.220 --> 36:06.670
have already arrived in Phoenix City.

36:06.670 --> 36:08.200
We need to hurry over there.

36:08.230 --> 36:08.880
If we had intercepted

36:08.880 --> 36:10.440
them on the way, it would've been fine.

36:10.440 --> 36:12.300
Now that they are in Phoenix City,

36:12.670 --> 36:14.730
I'm afraid a big fight is inevitable.

36:15.230 --> 36:17.070
Senior Bai, don't worry too much.

36:17.070 --> 36:18.440
They're just a group
of demonic cultivators.

36:18.440 --> 36:19.970
How can we be afraid of them?

36:20.550 --> 36:21.360
Makes sense.

36:23.800 --> 36:25.060
Demonic cultivators.

36:38.550 --> 36:39.350
You're awake.

36:40.280 --> 36:41.030
Mr. Lu.

36:42.190 --> 36:43.050
How do you feel?

36:43.960 --> 36:44.800
Much better.

36:52.230 --> 36:53.430
Still hurts a little.

36:54.590 --> 36:55.670
You were badly injured,

36:55.670 --> 36:56.930
so it naturally hurts.

36:57.670 --> 36:58.800
Since you're awake,

36:58.880 --> 37:01.080
why don't you take your medicine first?

37:26.630 --> 37:27.360
It's bitter.

37:27.960 --> 37:29.220
How could it be bitter?

37:30.360 --> 37:32.000
You can't even taste anything.

37:32.000 --> 37:33.230
How do you know it's not bitter?

37:33.230 --> 37:34.630
I made the prescription.

37:35.070 --> 37:36.800
Wouldn't I know if it's bitter?

37:38.320 --> 37:39.120
Alright then.

37:40.670 --> 37:41.320
I'll do it.

37:49.320 --> 37:50.360
Where are we?

37:52.110 --> 37:53.240
At a friend's house.

37:56.190 --> 37:57.720
How long have I been asleep?

37:58.030 --> 37:58.630
Five days.

37:59.710 --> 38:01.320
How did they die?

38:03.590 --> 38:05.120
I went to check their bodies

38:05.480 --> 38:06.960
and found they were
poisoned by a Gu curse,

38:06.960 --> 38:08.360
a very vicious type of Gu.

38:08.800 --> 38:09.660
Once poisoned,

38:10.000 --> 38:11.530
they can never get rid of it.

38:13.960 --> 38:15.800
Someone killed their life-binding Gu,

38:15.800 --> 38:16.920
so they died.

38:17.230 --> 38:19.160
Who killed their life-binding Gu?

38:19.870 --> 38:20.830
I don't know yet.

38:30.880 --> 38:31.610
Don't worry.

38:32.400 --> 38:33.160
I'm here.

38:51.510 --> 38:52.110
By the way,

38:53.400 --> 38:55.060
they destroyed the painting.

38:55.800 --> 38:56.460
You like it?

38:58.740 --> 38:59.970
If you really like it,

39:00.480 --> 39:02.110
I can draw another one for you.

39:02.110 --> 39:02.710
Really?

39:03.360 --> 39:04.160
That's great.

39:06.590 --> 39:07.400
From now on,

39:08.070 --> 39:09.550
how should I address you?

39:10.280 --> 39:10.940
Address me?

39:12.920 --> 39:14.670
Lord Lu, Mr. Lu—

39:14.840 --> 39:16.070
I can't call you those anymore.

39:16.070 --> 39:17.760
Calling you by your full name

39:18.190 --> 39:19.450
makes us seem distant.

39:20.110 --> 39:21.590
How do your close friends

39:21.800 --> 39:22.800
address you?

39:25.030 --> 39:26.480
When I was

39:26.480 --> 39:27.670
with my parents and master,

39:27.670 --> 39:28.670
I was still young.

39:29.070 --> 39:30.070
Besides Chu Ying,

39:30.170 --> 39:30.800
I don't really have

39:30.800 --> 39:31.860
any other friends.

39:32.510 --> 39:34.070
Su Taiyi calls me Master.

39:34.590 --> 39:36.710
Chu Ying just calls me Lu.

39:40.450 --> 39:42.540
Then from now on, I'll call you

39:43.870 --> 39:44.660
Qianqiao.

39:48.550 --> 39:49.350
What's wrong?

39:50.030 --> 39:51.030
You don't like it?

39:52.230 --> 39:52.710
Yes.

39:53.960 --> 39:54.920
I really like it.

39:55.720 --> 39:56.760
No one

39:57.150 --> 39:58.480
has ever called me that.

40:00.110 --> 40:02.110
I'll call you that from now on.

40:03.920 --> 40:04.520
Qianqiao.

40:18.390 --> 40:19.550
Here are the clothes you asked for.

40:19.550 --> 40:20.150
Thank you.

40:20.460 --> 40:21.440
Please help the lady inside

40:21.440 --> 40:22.800
change into these clothes.

40:22.800 --> 40:23.190
Okay.

41:15.110 --> 41:15.970
He's really...

41:20.110 --> 41:21.150
Time to eat.

41:25.550 --> 41:26.210
Not eating?

41:50.670 --> 41:51.360
Sister-in-law,

41:51.360 --> 41:52.160
you're awake.

41:52.960 --> 41:53.760
Who are you?

41:54.840 --> 41:55.770
Just call me Sha.

41:56.000 --> 41:56.860
This is my home.

41:57.150 --> 41:58.290
You were injured that day.

41:58.290 --> 41:59.420
Lu brought you back.

42:00.000 --> 42:00.550
I see.

42:01.000 --> 42:01.590
Thank you.

42:01.590 --> 42:02.280
Don't mention it.

42:02.280 --> 42:03.880
Lu and I are as close as brothers.

42:03.880 --> 42:05.190
His business is my business.

42:05.190 --> 42:06.550
His enemies are my enemies.

42:06.550 --> 42:07.190
His family...
